o, the Guide\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |1944\n|''[[Song of Russia]]''\n|Alexander Meschkov\n|\n|-\n|''[[Passage to Marseille]]''\n|Grandp\u00e8re\n|\n|-\n|''[[Till We Meet Again (1944 film)|Till We Meet Again]]''\n|Cabeau\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Conspirators (1944 film)|The Conspirators]]''\n|Miguel\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |1945\n|''[[A Royal Scandal (film)|A Royal Scandal]]''\n|Malakoff\n|\n|-\n|''[[Back to Bataan]]''\n|Se\u00f1or Buenaventura J. Bello\n|\n|-\n|''[[Paris Underground (film)|Paris Underground]]''\n|Pierre, the Undertaker\n|\n|-\n|''[[Scarlet Street]]''\n|Pop LeJon\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |1946\n|''[[Two Smart People]]''\n|Monsieur Jacques Dufour\n|\n|-\n|''[[A Scandal in Paris]]''\n|Uncle Hugo\n|\n|-\n|''[[Cloak and Dagger (1946 film)|Cloak and Dagger]]''\n|Polda\n|\n|-\n|1948\n|''[[To the Ends of the Earth (1948 film)|To the Ends of the Earth]]''\n|Commissioner Lum Chi Chow\n|\n|-\n|1950\n|''[[The Baron of Arizona]]''\n|Pepito\n|\n|-\n|1952\n|''[[Macao (film)|Macao]]''\n|Kwan Sum Tang\n|\n|-\n|1956\n|''[[While the City Sleeps (1956 film)|While the City Sleeps]]''\n|George \"Pop\" Pilski\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |1957\n|''[[Istanbul (film)|Istanbul]]''\n|Aziz Rakim\n|\n|-\n|''[[Monster from Green Hell]]''\n|Dr. Lorentz\n|\n|-\n|''[[I Was a Teenage Werewolf]]''\n|Pepe the Janitor\n|\n|-\n|''Sabu and the Magic Ring''\n|Old Fakir\n|\n|-\n|1958\n|''[[Twilight for the Gods]]''\n|Feodor Morris\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |1960\n|''[[Man on a String]]''\n|Sergei Mitrov\n|\n|-\n|''[[Beyond the Time Barrier]]''\n|The Supreme\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Magnificent Seven]]''\n|The Old Man\n|\n|-\n|''[[Cimarron (1960 film)|Cimarron]]''\n|Jacob Krubeckoff\n|\n|-\n|1961\n|''[[Mr. Sardonicus]]''\n|Henryk Toleslawski\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1962\n|''[[Escape from Zahrain]]''\n|Abdul\n|Uncredited<br>Posthumous release\n|-\n|''[[Taras Bulba (1962 film)|Taras Bulba]]''\n|Old Stepan\n|Posthumous release\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n!Role