\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1934\n|''[[Lake of Ladies]]''\n|Baron Dobbersberg\n|\n|-\n|''[[Count Woronzeff]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Petroff\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1935\n|''[[Le secret des Woronzeff]]''\n|\n|-\n|''Napol\u00e9on Bonaparte''\n|Trista Fleuri\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |1936\n|''[[Mayerling (1936 film)|Mayerling]]''\n|The Chief of Police\n|\n|-\n|''[[Under Western Eyes (1936 film)|Under Western Eyes]]''\n|Rector\n|\n|-\n|''[[Compliments of Mister Flow]]''\n|Merlow\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Lower Depths (1936 film)|The Lower Depths]]''\n|Kostylev\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\" |1937\n|''[[The Life of Emile Zola]]''\n|[[Paul C\u00e9zanne]]\n|\n|-\n|''[[Alcatraz Island (film)|Alcatraz Island]]''\n|The Flying Dutchman\n|\n|-\n|''[[Conquest (1937 film)|Conquest]]''\n|Dying Soldier\n|\n|-\n|''[[West of Shanghai]]''\n|Chow Fu-Shan\n|\n|-\n|''[[Expensive Husbands]]''\n|Andrew Brenner\n|\n|-\n|''[[Beg, Borrow or Steal]]''\n|Sascha\n|\n|-\n|''[[Tovarich (film)|Tovarich]]''\n|\n|Scenes deleted\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |1938\n|''[[Ars\u00e8ne Lupin Returns]]''\n|Ivan Pavloff\n|\n|-\n|''[[Blockade (1938 film)|Blockade]]''\n|Basil\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Amazing Dr. Clitterhouse]]''\n|Popus\n|\n|-\n|''[[Spawn of the North]]''\n|Dimitri\n|\n|-\n|''[[Ride a Crooked Mile]]''\n|Glinka\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |1939\n|''[[Juarez (1939 film)|Juarez]]''\n|Camilo\n|\n|-\n|''[[Sons of Liberty (film)|Sons of Liberty]]''\n|Jacob\n|Short film; uncredited\n|-\n|''[[The Real Glory]]''\n|The Datu\n|\n|-\n|1940\n|''[[Comrade X]]''\n|Michael Bastakoff\n|\n|-\n|1941\n|''[[Love Crazy (1941 film)|Love Crazy]]''\n|Dr. Klugle\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1942\n|''[[Crossroads (1942 film)|Crossroads]]''\n|Carlos Le Duc\n|Uncredited\n|-\n|''[[Road to Morocco]]''\n|Hyder Khan\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |1943\n|''[[Mission to Moscow]]''\n|President [[Mikhail Kalinin]]\n|\n|-\n|''[[Mr. Lucky (film)|Mr. Lucky]]''\n|Greek Priest\n|Uncredited\n|-\n|''[[For Whom the Bell Tolls (film)|For Whom the Bell Tolls]]''\n|Anselmo, the Guide\n|\n|-